   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="edition">
            <ab>
               <lb n="1"/>D<hi rend="tall">i</hi>s Manibus
            <lb n="2"/>
               <persName>
                  <name type="gentilicium" key="Maelia">Maeliae</name>
                  <name type="cognomen" key="Elaphe">Elaphe</name></persName>.
             <lb n="3"/>
               <expan><abbr>Vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan>
               <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nis</ex></expan>
               <num xml:lang="lat" value="4">IIII</num>
               <expan><abbr>mens</abbr><ex>ibus</ex></expan>
               <num value="10">X</num>.
            <lb n="4"/>
               <persName>
                  <name type="praenomen" key="Lucius">
                     <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan>
                  </name>
                  <name type="gentilicium" key="Maelius">Maelius</name>
                  <name type="cognomen" key="Felix">Felix</name>
               </persName> et
             <lb n="5"/>
               <persName>
                  <name type="gentilicium" key="Maelia">Maelia</name>
                  <name type="cognomen" key="Capriola">Capriola</name>
               </persName>
               <lb n="6"/>filiae dulcissimae 
             <lb n="7"/>fecerunt. 
            </ab>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>To the Divine Spirits of Maelia Elaphe. She lived for four years (and) ten
                    months. Lucius Maelius Felix and Maelia Capriola made (this) for (their) dearest
                    daughter. </p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Tall "I"s in the first I in the line (only) in lines 1 (Dis), 3 (vix), and 6 (filia). </p>
         </div>
